    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S in peerless condition. This example features the 3.8L flat-six M97 power plant with a verified clean bore-scope and zero over-rev incidents on the DME report. The 6-speed manual transaxle is paired with a factory-optioned limited-slip differential, delivering linear power through a perfectly balanced chassis. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and four-piston monobloc calipers, the mechanical feedback is surgical. Meticulously maintained with a fully documented service dossier, this vehicle retains its factory-correct tolerances and showroom-quality aesthetic. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
