    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive care: a 2019 BMW M5 Competition in a stunning Marina Bay Blue Metallic finish. This vehicle has been kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one and has never seen a drop of rain. The exterior is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero rock chips thanks to a professional full-body clear bra (PPF). Inside, the Silverstone full Merino leather remains in showroom condition\u2014absolutely no bolster wear, no creases, and it still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; every service has been performed strictly at authorized BMW centers, and I have the complete digital and physical service history ready for your review. With exceptionally low mileage, this vehicle drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight, powerful, and responsive. Every feature, from the Bowers & Wilkins sound system to the carbon fiber trim, is in perfect working order. I welcome and encourage any pre-purchase inspection from a mechanic of your choice to verify this car's pristine, collector-grade status.",
      "price": 46500.0,
